## 2. Analytics APIs (Programmatic Access)

For pulling data into your own dashboards, data warehouses, or BI tools.

Anthropic provides **two separate APIs** — which one you need depends on your plan:

| API | Plan | Key type | What it covers |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Claude Code Analytics API** | Claude Platform (API/Console) | Admin API key (`sk-ant-admin01-...`) | Daily per-user Claude Code productivity metrics |
| **Claude Enterprise Analytics API** | Claude Enterprise (claude.ai) | Analytics API key (created in claude.ai) | Org-wide engagement, adoption, cost across all Claude products |

> These key types are **not interchangeable** — an Admin API key cannot call the Enterprise Analytics API and vice versa.

---

### 2a. Claude Code Analytics API

| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| **Endpoint** | `GET https://api.anthropic.com/v1/organizations/usage_report/claude_code` |
| **Key type** | Admin API key — created at [Console > Settings > Admin keys](https://platform.claude.com/settings/admin-keys) |
| **Who can create key** | Organization Admin role |
| **Cost** | Free to use |
| **Docs** | [Claude Code Analytics API](https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/manage-claude/claude-code-analytics-api) |

**Metrics returned (daily, per user):**

| Field | Description |
|---|---|
| Sessions | Number of Claude Code sessions for the user on that day |
| Lines of code | Lines generated / accepted |
| Commits | Commits made during Claude Code sessions |
| Pull requests | PRs opened during Claude Code sessions |
| Tool acceptance | Rate at which tool suggestions were accepted |
| Token usage | Tokens consumed per model |
| Estimated cost | Cost estimate by model |

**Aggregation:** Daily only. For real-time, use the [OpenTelemetry integration](https://docs.anthropic.com).

---

### 2b. Claude Enterprise Analytics API

| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| **Base URL** | `https://api.anthropic.com/v1/organizations/analytics/` |
| **Key type** | Analytics API key — created at [claude.ai > Org settings > API](https://claude.ai/admin-settings/api-access) |
| **Who can create key** | Primary Owner |
| **Docs** | [Analytics APIs overview](https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/manage-claude/analytics-api) |
| **Help article** | [Get started with the Claude Enterprise Analytics API](https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13694757-get-started-with-the-claude-enterprise-analytics-api) |

**What it covers:**

| Data type | Granularity |
|---|---|
| User activity | Per-user daily metrics across chat, Claude Code, projects, files, artifacts |
| Active users | Org-level daily, weekly, monthly active users + seat counts |
| Claude Code activity | Sessions, commits, PRs, lines of code, tool actions |
| Project & connector usage | Adoption breakdowns for chat projects, skills, connectors |
| Cost & token reports | Per-user and org-level token usage and cost over time (usage-based plans) |

