## 3. Analytics Chat (New)

Ask Claude natural language questions about your own usage data.

| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| **What it is** | Chat interface that queries your org's analytics data |
| **Help article** | [Use analytics chat to ask Claude about usage](https://support.claude.com/en/articles/14729354-use-analytics-chat-to-ask-claude-about-usage) |

Example queries: *"Which teams have the highest acceptance rate this month?"*, *"Show me PR contribution trends for the last 4 weeks."*

