## 4. Key Limitations to Know

| Limitation | Detail |
|---|---|
| Scope | Only covers users within your claude.ai org. Console/API or third-party integration usage not included |
| Zero Data Retention | Contribution metrics unavailable if ZDR is enabled |
| GitHub requirement | Contribution metrics require GitHub Cloud, not GitHub Enterprise Server |
| Data delay | Enterprise Analytics API has a 3-day data delay. Not suitable for real-time monitoring |
| Historical data | Enterprise Analytics API data available from January 1, 2026 onwards |
| Individual plans | Usage analytics not available on individual Pro or Max plans |
| Min version | Users must be on Claude Code v2.0.28+ to appear in analytics |

