## 6. What Claude Does NOT Provide (You Need to Add)

These are gaps you'll need to cover with your own tooling:

| Gap | Suggested source |
|---|---|
| Code churn rate | Git analytics (GitClear, Waydev, custom script) |
| Defect injection rate | CI/CD pipeline + bug tracker correlation |
| PR review time delta | GitHub API or engineering analytics tool |
| Developer experience / satisfaction | Pulse survey (biweekly, 5 questions) |
| Task-type attribution (debugging vs greenfield) | Ticket tagging discipline in Jira/Linear |

